👋 About Me

I am a passionate Software Tester with a solid IT background, which allows me to understand systems from both technical and business perspectives. I specialize in identifying defects early in the software lifecycle and ensuring that applications meet high quality, reliability, and usability standards. I enjoy breaking systems to make them better — and I communicate issues clearly so developers can fix them efficiently.
